{"tid":807184,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[單車撚入] 求摺車推薦","createTime":"2018-09-05T10:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T16:59:33.000Z","uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fc5f3ec120419300b7296925f9619ae3f39075a5","tid":807184,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:17:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我最近想入部摺車<br />\n方便上地鐵/巴士，去遠啲既地方踩車<br />\n<br />\n但係新加坡local既單車鋪好少摺車選擇<br />\n我搵左3間，仲未搵到一部摺車岩心水<br />\n希望各位可以推薦一架俾我，我拎名去問代理/上網買<br />\n<br />\n我想要既野：<br />\n1.) 輕過15kg<br />\n2.) budget 4k hkd左右<br />\n3.) load 120kg以上，我85kg<br />\n4.) 摺完部車可以輕鬆推住走 (eg. Brompton / carryme)<br />\n<br />\n有好多摺車，摺完係咁樣，推推下好易側一面就跌落地：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tnLJWOv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtnLJWOv.png&h=d11e7fcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"886dc2e299fc50997ff161674ab00d1d36e3878f","tid":807184,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"Carryme"},{"pid":"a215ce7fc78717632e21775773a155dc3d594e69","tid":807184,"uid":3063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"060"},{"pid":"d4b696c7b1c37fd7793cd450893a3563ae8889e9","tid":807184,"uid":202354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:51:42.000Z","msg":"都係個幾間java Dahon birdy tern"},{"pid":"00ec50307965dd5c08642ef85f61613b62f94a46","tid":807184,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"886dc2e299fc50997ff161674ab00d1d36e3878f","tid":807184,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"Carryme"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T15:00:22.000Z","msg":"超budget好多啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9310c7a79ec8af6f9e924228cfc3e3856ca9c108","tid":807184,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"得 4K budget  都要求摺完方便 <